{"type":"text","timestamp":1775841394479,"sessionID":"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L","part":{"id":"prt_d78653b85001cUqv6IGsFmGdTB","messageID":"msg_d78652397001Jw5paRuJlo1LZa","sessionID":"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L","type":"text","text":"Done. Created `proposal.md` for AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework) with:\n\n- **Purpose**: HTTP service to expose AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRUD APIs\n- **Scope**: HTTP server, REST endpoints, client-go integration, middleware\n- **Impact Analysis**: Dependencies, consumers, risks\n- **Alternatives Considered**: net/http (selected), Gin/Echo, K8s aggregation, gRPC","time":{"start":1775841394477,"end":1775841394477}}}
